:::The Destrocons/Falcon/Snare:::

::They all arrive at the ruined Neocon base in Syria.  Falcon opens his 
cockpit for Neody to climb out of.  Snare and the Destrocons transform.  
Snare looks around at what used to be his home.  It was leveled, with 
cave-ins at every corner.  He then looks down and sees the bodies of 
Autojetter and Leozak, still reasonably intact::
Snare: Things sure have changed...
Ramjet: Hmm.  It will take a lot of work, but i think we might be able to 
turn this piece of slag into a base.
::They all wait for Like-Like and Cygnar to arrive::

--part1_f6.7f5f92b.27d9a031_boundary
